articles.author: Chris Willman
articles.title: Lady Gaga Joins U2 for ‘Shallow’ and Other Duets at Las Vegas’ Sphere - Variety
articles.description: Lady Gaga sang a pair of U2 numbers as well as her own 'Shallow' in an extended series of duets with Bono at Sphere in Las Vegas.
